What is requirement analysis
is the process of gathering, analyzing, documenting and validating what a system, product or project should do.
OBJECTIVES
1. undeestanding stakeholders needs clearly
2.define functional requirements
3.define non-functional requirements
reduce misunderstandings between clients,users and developers.
4.avoid costly changes.
STEPS IN REQUIREMENT ANALYSIS
1. requirement gathering
2.  requirement    categorization
3.  requirement     analysis and modelling
4.  requirement     documentation
5. requirement      validation
6.  requirement     management
CHALLENGES
ambiguous requirements
conflicts
scope creep
unclear business objectives
BENEFITS
reduce project failure risk
improve customer satisfication
saves time.
